  "detailed_description": "<h1>加入玩家大家庭！</h1><p>欢迎加入游戏官方QQ交流群，了解我们的最新动态，一起讨论相关话题。<br>风铃工作室粉丝QQ群：<strong>791432683</strong><br>风域游戏咕咕咕群：<strong>224508161</strong></p><br><h1>更多风域家游戏~！</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>●故事(STORY)●</strong></h2>《梦染深秋》是一款现代都市悬疑视觉小说游戏。2006年的秋天，集川市发生的犯罪案件日益增多，毒品及暴力犯罪屡禁不止，当地警方对于犯罪团伙的调查迟迟得不到进展。主人公“林秋”作为一名在校学生，原本与那些犯罪活动并无瓜葛，但却在某次散步时意外目睹了犯罪现场，此时他才发现自己早已身处漩涡之中。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571280/extras/74b79f80a597cf8a740d22458e71fef0.avif?t=1749636956\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>●角色介绍(CHARACTER)●</strong></h2><strong>夏梦染</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571280/extras/514bc8ee30f499b3e1aef890f1215051.avif?t=1749636956\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>满春</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571280/extras/9c61a0875adcb33e87b0a7ee5cce0855.avif?t=1749636956\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>李雪东</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571280/extras/8f4f4f0b18332876ddde1746ca429655.avif?t=1749636956\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>胡桃夹子</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571280/extras/72c624c523afb65e34f2a91ee1300bee.avif?t=1749636956\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>●游戏特点(GAME FEATURES)●</strong></h2>※双线路分支，剧情悬疑氛围浓郁，反转不断<br><br>※20+张精美CG、70+张游戏背景、辅以高完成度演出，视觉效果出色<br>※知名优秀CV献声、30+首BGM，营造超沉浸式游戏体验",
